Heat oven to 350 degrees F. Mix Crust, butter, sugar and nuts; spread onto parchment-covered baking sheet. Bake 5 to 6 min. or until toasted; cool. Meanwhile, prepare Filling and Meringue Topping as directed on package. Spoon Filling into 12 dessert dishes; top with Crust mixture, berries and Meringue Topping. Refrigerate 1 hour.